{
  "stem": "4967.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "People used to get sores, bleeding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "They used to get gangrene.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "They used to die like flies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "You're not only gangrene in the feet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "It used to swell up the body.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "You used to get sores on the body, bleeding, didn't sleep at night, pain, screaming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Wake up at night, used to be terrible screams.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "Terrible, terrible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "It made my [GERMAN], my-- my still used to be long shoes, like military boots.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And I was a rich man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "I had gold with me and I had a watch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "This what I survived with this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And in the lager, in the main camp that I was, luckily when we came to Germany, they didn't send us Dachau main camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "We came straight to working camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "In the main camp, if I would arrived in the main camp, I wouldn't have survived a day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "They took away the children straight away, I heard, and they liquidated them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "Now, I came to this working camp number one in Dachau, Kaufering, Dachau, my father, myself, and my brother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "And my brother didn't have a job yet, was not [INAUDIBLE] job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "He was younger than me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "I managed to be the [INAUDIBLE] in the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "And my brother was not advised to go out to work outside the camp because they'll notice straight away a young child is going to work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "So he remained in-- in the-- in this camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "After a month or so, they lined everybody up in this camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "And a German walked around and took the numbers from sick people, young people, and children, and my brother's number too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "And after two hours, they took everybody off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "They didn't say why they took the numbers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "But we knew already why they take the numbers for.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
